---
title: One-Pot Peanut Beef Stir-Fry with Noodles and Veggies
description: Velvety and nutty, this satay-inspired beef noodle stir-fry captures the fragrant flavours of Southeast Asia in an easy, one-pot recipe that the whole family will love.

